      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's interesting. you mentioned those \"general trends\"—can you expand on that? like, do you have any specific studies or data points that back up the idea that certain groups are naturally wired for explosive vs endurance stuff? i just want to make sure i'm not overgeneralizing when i talk to my clients.",
